    "Metrics Reloaded targets image analysis problems that can be interpreted as classification tasks at image, object or pixel level, namely image-level classification, object detection, semantic segmentation and instance segmentation tasks.",
    "To improve the user experience, we implemented the framework in the Metrics Reloaded online tool.",
    "Following the convergence of ML methodology across application domains, Metrics Reloaded fosters the convergence of validation methodology.",
    "Its applicability is demonstrated for various biomedical use cases.",
    "Automatic image processing with ML is gaining increasing traction in biological and medical imaging research and practice."
